<quantity box="[607,715,331,355]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.45" metricValueMax="3.0" metricValueMin="1.9" pageId="32" pageNumber="539" unit="cm" value="24.5" valueMax="30.0" valueMin="19.0">19–30 cm</quantity>
long, glabrous, ligulate. It is characterized by its inflores- cence with 2 terminal branches, with green and glabrous spikelets.
</paragraph>
